{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──三个月后。\n整体院营业顺利。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "老师…你好…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "奈奈。这周也来了呢。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "是的…那个…想再…拜托您…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "我想肩膀应该已经好了…你却还来。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "唔……那个…身体…渴望着…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "普通的按摩…已经…不够了…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "这样啊。今天也是老样子的疗程？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "…是的。麻烦您了。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──治疗中"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "outfit": "naked",
      "text": "嗯…♡啊啊…♡",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_006"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "身体已经变得反应很快了呢。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "好、好害羞…这么…快就…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_007"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "但是很舒服吧？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "…是的…很…舒服…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_008"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──过了一会儿"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "哈…哈…♡",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_009"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "今天也很有感觉呢。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "那个……",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_010"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "嗯？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "…作为答谢…我也…给老师按摩…可以吗…？",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_011"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "咦？奈奈给我按摩？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "是、是的…因为总是被您弄得很舒服…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_012"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_lookaway_openmouth",
      "text": "我也想…让老师…舒服…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_013"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "这样啊。那…就拜托你了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "好的…用嘴…给老师的…按摩哦…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_014"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "咦？用嘴？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "虽然不知道能不能做好……",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_015"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（居然主动到这种地步…完全沦陷了…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "奈奈害羞地伸手向裤子。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_closeeyes_closemouth",
      "text": "…打扰了…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_016"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "奈奈用微微颤抖的手，取出了我的肉棒。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "啊…已经…这么…♡",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_017"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "…唔姆…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_018"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "嗯、呼…舔…啊姆……唔啾…♡ 舔……嗯…唔啾…♡",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_019"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（这么努力地为我…真可爱…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "…噗哈…♡",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_020"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "老师…怎么…样…？",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_021"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "非常舒服哦。奈奈，谢谢你。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_happysmile",
      "text": "太好了…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_022"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "奈奈害羞却又用期待的眼神看着这边。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "那个…老师…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_023"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "嗯？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "接下来……用…用小穴，按摩…可以吗…？",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_024"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "哦。终于开始主动说这种话了呢。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "因为……身体…发疼…忍不住了…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_025"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "真拿你没办法。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "谢谢您…♡",
      "voiceFile": "ending_develop_max_026"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "奈奈的身体已被完全开发，没有快感就无法满足。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "即使害羞，也会主动索求。\n那与其说是信赖关系，不如说是身体渴求的本能欲望。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "【DEVELOP MAX END - 被开发的身体】",
      "triggerEnding": "develop_max"
    }
  ]
}
